    19→//! SupplyWarehouseCripplingBehavior - Rust conversion of C++ SupplyWarehouseCripplingBehavior
    20→//! 
    21→//! Behavior that Disables the building on ReallyDamaged edge state, and manages an Update timer to heal
    22→//! Original Author: Graham Smallwood, September 2002
    23→//! Rust conversion: 2025
    24→
    25→use std::sync::{Arc, Mutex, RwLock};
    26→use crate::common::{
    27→    Real, UnsignedInt, Int, Bool,
    28→    Thing, ModuleData,
    29→};
